.TH OWL 8 "August 2024" "owl 0.1.0" "System Administration Commands"
.SH NAME
owl \- modern AUR helper and package manager for Arch Linux
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B owl
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fICOMMAND\fR] [\fIARGUMENTS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B owl
is a modern AUR helper and package manager for Arch Linux that provides config management and setup script automation. It can install packages from both official repositories and the AUR, manage dotfiles, run setup scripts, and handle system services.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B apply
Install packages, copy configs, and run setup scripts (default command)
.TP
.B dry-run, dr
Preview what would be done without making changes
.TP
.B dots
Check and sync only dotfiles configurations
.TP
.B search, s
Search for packages in repositories and AUR
.TP
.B install, i, S
Install packages from repositories or AUR
.TP
.B upgrade, u
Upgrade all packages to latest versions
.TP
.B info, Si
Show detailed information about a package
.TP
.B query, q, Q
Query installed packages
.TP
.B uninstall
Remove all managed packages and configs
.TP
.B gendb
Generate VCS database for development packages
.TP
.B help, --help
Show help message
.TP
.B version, -v
Show version information
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --verbose
Show full command output instead of progress spinners
.TP
.B --no-spinner
Disable loading animations
.TP
.B --dry-run
Preview changes without making them
.TP
.B --devel
Include development packages in upgrade
.TP
.B --foreign
List foreign (AUR) packages
.SH CONFIGURATION
Configuration files should be placed in
.IR ~/.owl/ .
.TP
.I ~/.owl/main.owl
Global configuration file
.TP
.I ~/.owl/hosts/{hostname}.owl
Host-specific configuration overrides
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B owl
Apply all configurations (default)
.TP
.B owl search firefox
Search for firefox packages
.TP
.B owl install yay
Install yay from AUR
.TP
.B owl upgrade --devel
Upgrade including development packages
.TP
.B owl info discord
Show information about discord package
.TP
.B owl query --foreign
List AUR packages
.TP
.B owl dots
Sync only dotfiles configurations
.TP
.B owl dots --dry-run
Preview dotfiles changes
.TP
.B owl gendb
Generate VCS database for development packages
.TP
.B owl dry-run
Preview config changes
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.owl/
Configuration directory
.TP
.I ~/.owl/.state/
State and cache directory
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR pacman (8),
.BR makepkg (8),
.BR yay (8)
.SH AUTHOR
Written for the Arch Linux community.
